<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 08:11:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的走狗改变了对哈马斯协议的态度，但他的极右翼盟友可能不会加入他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lackeys-change-tune-on-hamas-deal-but-his-far-right-allies-likely-wont-agree/00000191-66d0-d876-a5ff-e7f8454a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的喉舌在一周内突然改变了对与哈马斯释放人质协议的看法，这可能对谈判至关重要，但总理的极右翼盟友加入他们的可能性并不高</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:59:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lackeys-change-tune-on-hamas-deal-but-his-far-right-allies-likely-wont-agree/00000191-66d0-d876-a5ff-e7f8454a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么加沙的费城路线和拉法对于埃及和人质交易如此重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/gazas-philadelphi-route-and-rafah-crossing-key-to-egypts-position-in-cease-fire-talks/00000191-671f-d1ca-adb9-6fff12880000</link><description>虽然以色列从加沙完全撤军不在停火谈判现阶段的议程上，但费城路线和加沙-西奈边境拉法过境点的地位对埃及的立场至关重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:58:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/gazas-philadelphi-route-and-rafah-crossing-key-to-egypts-position-in-cease-fire-talks/00000191-671f-d1ca-adb9-6fff12880000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列，布林肯表示现在“可能是加沙人质交易的最后机会”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article-live/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-67da-d3bf-a3b1-efff74eb0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦卫生部：以色列国防军在约旦河西岸开火造成四人受伤 ■ 一名携带爆炸装置的男子在特拉维夫被杀；警察、辛贝特正在调查可能的恐怖主义 ■ 以色列国防军正在追捕在约旦河西岸杀害以色列保安人员的袭击者 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在加沙被火箭弹重伤 ■ 拜登：我们不会放弃停火，这仍然是可能的 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：我们可以对某些事情不能灵活变通；军事和外交压力是释放人质的途径</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 23:47:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article-live/hamas-new-u-s-proposal-accommodates-netanyahus-demands-prevents-deal/00000191-67da-d3bf-a3b1-efff74eb0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最高法院，不到 5% 的法律职员不是犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/at-israels-supreme-court-less-than-5-percent-of-all-law-clerks-arent-jewish/00000191-670c-d772-a9d5-6fbcc3ae0000</link><description>以色列最高法院在过去两年半中授予了 134 名书记员职位。不到百分之五的学生被授予非犹太人——绝大多数人在特拉维夫大学或希伯来大学学习</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 22:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-19/ty-article/.premium/at-israels-supreme-court-less-than-5-percent-of-all-law-clerks-arent-jewish/00000191-670c-d772-a9d5-6fbcc3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>在尼尔奥兹会议上，以色列人质的亲属要求商界领袖、公众采取行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/at-nir-oz-conference-hostages-relatives-demand-action-by-business-leaders-public/00000191-670c-d876-a5ff-e72cc18f0000</link><description>退休将军和商界领袖聚集在基布兹召开“全国紧急会议”，敦促内塔尼亚胡立即签署协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 20:51:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/at-nir-oz-conference-hostages-relatives-demand-action-by-business-leaders-public/00000191-670c-d876-a5ff-e72cc18f0000</guid></item><item><title>国防部官员认为特拉维夫爆炸是针对犹太教堂的恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/man-with-bomb-killed-in-tel-aviv-blast-police-shin-bet-probing-possible-terror-attack/00000191-6735-d3bf-a3b1-efb75b7f0000</link><description>特拉维夫地区指挥官、警司佩雷茨·阿马尔在现场表示，携带炸弹身亡的男子的身份对于了解爆炸本质上是犯罪还是恐怖分子至关重要</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 20:42:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/man-with-bomb-killed-in-tel-aviv-blast-police-shin-bet-probing-possible-terror-a