r-right-ministers-who-hail-settler-violence/00000191-65e6-dda8-af9b-65e6b4450000</link><description>定居者暴力持续不减的时间越长，后果就越严重，国际领导人采取自己的惩罚措施就越有道理</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 18:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-18/ty-article/.highlight/america-is-coming-for-israels-far-right-ministers-who-hail-settler-violence/00000191-65e6-dda8-af9b-65e6b4450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列保安人员在约旦河西岸袭击中被巴勒斯坦人杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-guard-killed-by-palestinian-in-west-bank-attack/00000191-6687-d772-a9d5-6ebf47430000</link><description>袭击者用锤子将 38 岁的吉迪恩·佩里 (Gideon Perry) 打成致命伤，然后偷走了他的武器并驾车逃跑。以色列军队仍在追捕嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:41:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-guard-killed-by-palestinian-in-west-bank-attack/00000191-6687-d772-a9d5-6ebf47430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国家检察官将领导对定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄事件的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-investigation-into-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village/00000191-6669-deb0-ab91-f7fd846f0000</link><description>在对吉特的突袭中，一名巴勒斯坦人被枪杀，但没有逮捕任何人，国防机构的初步调查表明，预备役士兵可能在现场袖手旁观</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:35:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-investigation-into-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village/00000191-6669-deb0-ab91-f7fd846f0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们之间有一堵冰墙”：罗宋汤地带的阿拉伯和犹太青少年结下了不解之缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/there-was-an-ice-wall-between-us-arab-and-jewish-teens-bond-in-the-borscht-belt/00000191-650d-d301-ad91-f57f9dfb0000</link><description>在卡茨基尔山度过一个夏天后，来自以色列的阿拉伯青少年回到了一个在战前很久就被种族隔离的动荡国家。组织者希望他们的对话能够产生影响</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 17:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/there-was-an-ice-wall-between-us-arab-and-jewish-teens-bond-in-the-borscht-belt/00000191-650d-d301-ad91-f57f9dfb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 317 天：以色列国家检察官将领导对约旦河西岸定居者骚乱的调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-317-israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-probe-of-west-bank-settler-riot/00000191-6630-d398-a7f5-ff70f9370000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士告诉沙特日报《Al Sharq》，目前正在讨论的停火提案“完全违背”哈马斯 7 月同意的协议 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列愿意在谈判中的某些问题上保持灵活性 ■ 美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列，将于周一与内塔尼亚胡会面，讨论确保加沙停战的努力 ■ 这是战争开始 317 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 16:54:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-317-israels-state-prosecutor-to-lead-probe-of-west-bank-settler-riot/00000191-6630-d398-a7f5-ff70f9370000</guid></item><item><title>“他们是来杀人的”：以色列定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄后，当地人担心没有人来拯救他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-locals-fear-theres-no-one-to-save-them/00000191-65d2-d3bf-a3b1-edf7aaa40000</link><description>周四，以色列定居者在约旦河西岸吉特村杀害了一名 23 岁男子，当地居民表示，这次袭击是一次精心策划的袭击，他们担心还会再次发生</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 15:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/after-settler-attack-on-palestinian-village-locals-fear-theres-no-one-to-save-them/00000191-65d2-d3bf-a3b1-edf7aaa40000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列在高级官员被杀之前破坏了真主党的通信网络</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/report-israel-breached-hezbollahs-communications-network-before-top-officials-killing/00000191-65f3-dda8-af9b-65f3cde50000</link><description>据《华尔街日报》报道，福阿德·舒克 (Fuad Shukr) 在以色列袭击导致他死亡之前接到电话，告诉他该去哪里</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 15:09:08 GMT</pubDate><guid i