5c63-dd29-a7f3-7d6bdb240000</guid></item><item><title>现在是拜登的表演：他能引导以色列和哈马斯达成加沙协议吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-trying-to-talk-a-deal-into-existence-but-a-breakthrough-isnt-yet-on-the-horizon/00000191-61ab-d993-a5d7-ebef1ef70000</link><description>美国总统正试图营造积极情绪，希望实现加沙停火并挫败伊朗袭击，但相关人士却不那么乐观 ■ 即使没有全面战争，以色列北部居民的生活也是难以忍受的与真主党合作 ■ 右翼对约旦河西岸致命定居者骚乱的谴责远没有令人信服</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 03:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-is-trying-to-talk-a-deal-into-existence-but-a-breakthrough-isnt-yet-on-the-horizon/00000191-61ab-d993-a5d7-ebef1ef70000</guid></item></channel></rss>